37361>>>        //  Hide header & apply nice background style
37361>>>        Send HideHeader to ghoWebApp
37362>>>        WebSet psCSSClass of ghoWebApp to "LoginBackground"
37363>>>    End_Procedure
37364>>>    
37364>>>End_Object
