38864>>>        Get HasRecord of hoDD to bHasRecord
38865>>>
38865>>>        // let's hide all buttons and then Show the ones we want
38865>>>        WebSet pbRender of oEditBtn to False
38866>>>        WebSet pbRender of oSaveBtn to False
38867>>>        WebSet pbRender of oCancelChangesBtn to False
